{"tid":2194602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥稱全民檢測將找出1500名隱形患者","createTime":"2020-09-08T15:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T10:55:17.000Z","uid":19552,"like":131,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"2dfeff3e3812dba8dcd705b466687a4f05c4f547","tid":2194602,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:05:33.000Z","msg":"不惜工本、虛耗資源的全民檢測下周二展開。計劃唯一目標，就是揪出行政長官林鄭月娥8月7日推算的1,500名武漢肺炎隱形病人。但綜合傳染病專家、資深醫務化驗師及公院醫生的沙盤推演，若一切如林鄭所料，1,500名病人到9月會變成沒傳染力、有抗體的病人，已非檢測要找的目標；即使他們傳播了病毒，到9月或僅剩270多名具傳染力的患者，但衞生署8月7日起已找了241名無病徵病人。立法會議員狠批，專家分析揭示全民檢測只是一場巨大騙局，「呢場係林鄭創造出嚟嘅科學&hellip;&hellip;成個劇情都係佢講出嚟」，只為向中央臉上貼金。"},{"pid":"39c048558c9c6336904c5a5e8013558a59557046","tid":2194602,"uid":83177,"like":125,"dislike":0,"score":125,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:09:41.000Z","msg":"林鄭：無限延期，測到有1500為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2050071b9eaed5d39b22ad58dc73d7883d9913","tid":2194602,"uid":37596,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:12:49.000Z","msg":"擺明要DNA ONLY,計劃通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e98a8512f173e19a1e6081a4d5953690a201575","tid":2194602,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:13:37.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全 (簡易版)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2194107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2194107</a><br />\n<br />\n樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0576b268f1513c905c6d939aefaba03aeac7857","tid":2194602,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b2050071b9eaed5d39b22ad58dc73d7883d9913","tid":2194602,"uid":37596,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:12:49.000Z","msg":"擺明要DNA ONLY,計劃通<i